night at 8pm Eastern, Sabrar (from Epic Shadows) will be attempting his final epic battle for Innoruk's Curse (Shadowknight Epic) in the City of Mist.  Here is the basic rundown of Lhranc as posted by ludarian:<br><br>60 Shadowknight<br>Harm Touch = 1000<br>Melee Attack = 350ish<br>Proc = 500 lifetap<br>HP = 17k<br>MR = all (with the exception of AA related abilities, such as Manaburn)<br>FR CR = Can be hit with LURE NUKES ONLY after he is debuffed<br><br>Considering all that is at stake if we wipe, we are asking as much help as we can get.  I hear his lifetap makes him particularly nasty.   And if seeing a Shadowknight Epic is not enough, I will be bringing plenty of alcohol, for naked races in CoM after.  For you Ranger/Druid types, Erwin will be leading a hit on the Reavers after for the all coveted Jade Reavers.<br><br>More info can be found here:<br>[url]http://boards.gamers.com/messages/message_view-topic.asp?name=VazAlliance&id=zzmvi[/url] <p><center><img src="http://www.vu.union.edu/~berardc/Nerpsig.gif" width=500 height=60><br><font size=2><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=180392">54 Half-Elven Tunarean Pathfinder</a>  | <a href="http://www.epicshadows.com">Epic Shadows</a> | Vazaelle</font></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub78.ezboard.com/ukalenie.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kalenie </A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hero</span><br>  Posts: 281<br> <font color=#00F500>(7/31/02 6:30:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub78.ezboard.com/fwalkersofvazaellefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=974.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.lby3.com/eq/walkers/kalenie.gif WIDTH=92 HEIGHT=146 ></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Final Shadowknight Epic Hit</span><hr size=1> Bah, you wont wipe on this guy. Dont you know SK are weenies<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img 